properties.Name: EquifaxConsumerCollectionAccount
properties.Description: Accounts which have been sent to a collection agency and have not been paid.

Columns.Name: DateReported
Columns.Description: The date the information was reported.

Columns.Name: DateAssigned
Columns.Description: The date the account was assigned to the collection agency.

Columns.Name: LastPaymentDate
Columns.Description: The date of the last payment.

Columns.Name: Comment
Columns.Description: A comment related to the collection account.

Columns.Name: EquifaxCreditorClassificationTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Equifax Creditor Classification Type.

Columns.Name: EquifaxCollectionAccountStatusTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Equifax Collection Account Status Type.

Columns.Name: EquifaxCollectionAccountOwnershipTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Equifax collection account ownership type.
